This file serves as a short-term roadmap for the project.
It will be updated regularly as new features are planned and implemented.


Upcoming Features
=================
+ Add boundaries so worm cannot go off screen
+ Add collision detection for worm body
+ Add apples to grow worm
+ Add basic obstacles
+ Animate apples
+ Enable apples to move around autonomously


Implemented
===========
2015-12-21 - Display an empty window
2016-01-14 - Control a rectangle with the arrow keys
2016-01-14 - Control a worm with the arrow keys
